{
  "texts": [
    "ML-based techniques for processing digitized waveform data have been rapidly developed.",
    "However, such digital records are available only for the last quarter of the period since the beginning of seismometer observations (Wang et al. 2019b).",
    "Past seismic activity should be investigated using analog records to assess the history of long-period seismic cycles.",
    "Although there are few examples, some important attempts have been reported.",
    "Furumura et al. (2023) applied a CNN network to digitize analog, strongmotion seismographs recorded on smoked paper."
  ]
}